labels.shortDescription: Why Start with a New Repository?
labels.value: Why Start with a New Repository?

Work in progress in your dev or hotfix Environments can move through your Pipeline by using commit and promotion deployments as usual. However, if there are changes in intermediate Environments, such as integration, testing, or staging Environments, then the Pipeline Initializer can help you to identify those changes and add them to User Stories, so that you can promote and deploy those changes through your Pipeline whenever you are ready.
Is there work in progress in your intermediate Environments?
When an environment sync is happening, any work in progress will be ignored in the following environments. Copado won't give the option to resolve conflicts and will apply a "source wins" strategy.
